    <p align="left">1 . Jesu Kristu ari muhupenyu hwemunhu uyu saMuponisi.&nbsp;<br>
    2. Jesu Kristu ari pachigaro chekutonga, ari kutonga hupenyu hwake.&nbsp;<br>
    3. &quot;Ini&quot; ave muranda anoterera Jesu Kristu.&nbsp;<br>
    4. Hupenyu hwemuKristu uyu hunotanga kuratidza chibereko cheMweya zvakanyana
    apo anodzidza&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; kubvumira Mweya Mutsvene kuti amutungamirire.&nbsp;<br>
    Kana MuKristu asina kuzadzwa neMweya M'tsvene anonzi...</p>
    <p align="center"><b>MUKRISTU ANOZVITONGA PACHAKE</b></p>
    <p align="left">MuKristu anozvitonga pachake (anoda nyika) anehanya
    nekuzvifadza iye pachake kupfuura kufadza Mwari. MuKristu anozvitonga
    pachake akafanana nemwana anongoda kuita zvaanoda iye - sezvinongoita munhu
    wenyika (munhu asiri muKristu).</p>
    <p align="left"><b>Maererano neMuKristu anozvitonga pachake Bhaibheri
    rinoti;</b></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font color="#5D5ED4">&quot;Ini hama dzangu ndakange
    ndisingagone kutaura nemi sokutaura kwandinoita nevanhu veMweya kwete, asi
    sokutaura kwandinoita nevanhu venyama, vachiri vacheche muna Kristu.
    Ndakakupai mukaka kuti munwe venyama, nokuti zvapachine godo pakati penyu
    negakava kohamuzi venyama muchifamba nenzira yevanhu here?&quot; I Vakorinte
    3:1-3</font></b></p>
