    <p align="left"><b>MUKRISTU ANOZVITONGA PACHAKE ANGAZADZWE NAMWEYA&nbsp;<br>
 MUTSVENE SEIKO?</b> <br>
    <br>
    <b>
    TINOZADZWA NAMWEYA MUTSVENE NEKUTENDA</b></p>
    <p>Tinova vaKristu nekutenda kuna Jesu Kristu saMuponisi. Saizvozvo
    tinozadzwa neMweya Mutsvene nekutenda. Zvingaitike iye zvino uno kuti
    ubvumire Mweya Mutsvene kuti akuzadze (akutonge)</p>
    <p>Parie zvinhu zvitatu zvaungaite:</p>
    <p><b>1. REURURA ZVIVI ZVAKO.&nbsp;</b><br>
    <b><font color="#5D5ED4">&quot;Kana tichizvireurura zvizi zvedu, iye
    wakatendeka, wakarurama nokudaro kuti unotikanganwira zvivi zvedu
    nekutinatsa pakusarurama kwose.&quot; I Johane l:9&nbsp;</font></b></p>
    <p><b>Kureurura zvinoreva kuti. . .&nbsp;</b><br>
    a. Unobvumirana naMwari kuti watadza.&nbsp;<br>
    b. Unotenda Mwari nekuti akukanganwira akakuchenesa kuburi kidza nemuna Jesu
    Kristu.&nbsp;<br>
    c. Unobva pazvivi zvako wova munhu anoterera Mwari (kutendeuka)</p>
    <p><b>2. ZVIPIRE KUNA MWARI.</b>&nbsp;</p>
    <p><b><font color="#5D5ED4">&quot;Uye musapa zvivi mitezo yenyu, kuti dzive
    nhumbi dzokuita zvisakarurama; asi muzvipei imi kunaMwari savanhu vakararama
    kuvakafa, nemitezo yenyu kuti dzive nhumbi dzokurarama kunaMwari, &quot;
    VaRoma 6:13&nbsp;</font></b></p>
    <p>Kuti tigare hupenyu hwekuzadzwa neMweya Mutsvene tinofanira kubvumira
    Jesu Kristu kuti atonge zvose zvatinoita.&nbsp;</p>
    <p>Anofanira kutonga mari yedu, nguva yatinenge tisina basa rekuita, basa
    redu, pamwechete nehukama hwedu nehama, neshamwari.</p>
    <p><b>3. TENDA (BVUMA) KUTI MWARI ANOKUZADZA NEMWEYA WAKE MUTSVENE.</b>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>Mwari anokuzadza neMweya Wake Mutsvene kana wavimba naye kuti
    azviite.&nbsp;</p>
    <p>Pane mazwi maviri anokosha kurangarira:&nbsp;</p>
    <p><b>KURAIRA KWAMWARI:&nbsp;</b></p>
    <p><b><font color="#5D5ED4">&quot;Uye regai kudhakwa nedoro, nokuti ndipo
    pane kusazvidzora, asi muzadzwe neMweya.&quot; &nbsp;VaEfeso 5:18&nbsp;</font></b></p>
    <p><b>CHIVIMBISO CHAMWARI:&nbsp;</b></p>
    <p><b><font color="#5D5ED4">&quot;Kutsunga kwatinako paari ndokuku, kwokuti
    kana tichikumbira chinhu sezvaanoda lye, anonzwa zvatinoreva. Zvino kana
    tichiziva kuti anonzwa zvatinoreva pane zvatinenge takumbira, tinozivawo
    kuti tatowana izvozvo zvatakumbira&quot; I Johane 5:14,15.</font></b> <br>
    </p>
    <center>

<center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p align="center"><b><font size="4">TINOZADZWA
          NEMWEYA MUTSVENE NEKUTENDA.</font></b></p>
        <p><b>Imwe nzira yaungaratidze nayo kutenda kwako kunamata.</b> </p>
          <p align="center">ZVIMWE UNGADE KUNAMATA SEIZVI:</p>
        <blockquote>
          <p><b><font color="#5D5ED4">&quot;Ishe Jesu ndinoda kuti Imi mutonge
          hupenyu hwangu. Ndanga ndichitonga hupenyu hwangu pachangu, uye
          ndinobvumirana nemi kuti ichochi chivi. Zvino ndinobva pachivi ichi,
          ndichizvipira kwamuri, kuti ndikutererei. Ndinotenda nokuti
          mandikanganwira. Zvino ndinoterera kuraira kwenyu nekuvimba nemi kuti
          mundizadze neMweya wenyu Mutsvene.&quot;</font></b>
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <p>Unoda here kukumbira Mwari kuti akuzadze nekutonga hupenyu
        hwako?&nbsp; </p>
        <p>Ungade kunamata muramato uyu iye zvino here? </p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b>NZIRA YOKUZIVA NAYO KUTI WAZADZWA NEMWEYA MUTSVENE</b></p>
          <p>Wakumbira Mwari kuti akuzadze neMweya Mutsvene here? Unoziva here
          kuti wazadzwa neMvveya Mutsvene? Ungazive kuti wazadzwa kuburikidza
          nekutenda (Kuvimba) nechivimbiso chaMwari chiri muBhaibheri.&nbsp;</p>
          <p>Mufananidzo uyu wechitima unoratidza kushanda kwechokwadi chiri
          muBhaibheri, kutenda, uye zvaunonzwa munyama yako muhupenyu hwako
          hwechiKristu.</p>
    </center>
</center>
